Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.78,0:00:03.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年也是美好的一年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.72,0:00:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在今年的最後 還是要做「那個」才行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.89,0:00:07.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做「那個」？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.69,0:00:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美好的一年要結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.16,0:00:12.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛麗絲…這麼一想確實會讓人感到寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.16,0:00:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但心中的美好是永遠都不會消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.36,0:00:18.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人害羞的台詞 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.38,0:00:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小愛 今天是24月31日 天晴 有時下雪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.88,0:00:42.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來到AQUA後的第二個除夕夜就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:00:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷 可是空氣很舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.03,0:00:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在AQUA度過的第二個春夏秋冬裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.24,0:01:01.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所度過的每一天都如同寶物般閃閃發光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,順帶一提 在地球上聖誕節是大家一起過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.78,0:01:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除夕則是與家人一起過的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.05,0:01:13.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在新威尼斯卻相反
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:14.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟家人一起過聖誕節
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.12,0:01:16.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟朋友一起過除夕才是主流
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.72,0:01:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以今天我們要去聖馬可廣場
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.33,0:01:21.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟大家一起過除夕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.83,0:01:26.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦…艾莉西亞前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.23,0:01:28.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:31.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年我也好興奮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.67,0:01:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.98,0:03:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬢子好慢啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.05,0:03:30.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虧人家這麼早來幫艾莉西亞小姐佔位置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.89,0:03:32.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.99,0:03:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曉先生 伍迪先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.10,0:03:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會不會 快請坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.73,0:03:45.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早已為艾莉西亞小姐佔好座位了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:48.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.64,0:03:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.84,0:03:52.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新威尼斯的除夕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.78,0:03:56.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全城的人都會聚集到聖馬可廣場
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:03:59.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主要活動是新年倒數
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:03.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後一直到新年日出之時
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.92,0:04:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人們都會為慶祝新年而徹夜狂歡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.03,0:04:10.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有在這個時候 大家才會不拘禮節
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.26,0:04:14.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直就是喧鬧而盛大的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:21.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想讓小愛也來這裡看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.97,0:04:24.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 所以我來看了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.84,0:04:28.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我剛才好像聽到小愛的聲音了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.22,0:04:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:33.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈里 我來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.26,0:04:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞利亞社長 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.39,0:04:43.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.00,0:04:49.93,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(320,270)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那個 純白的早晨…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.77,0:04:55.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦～ 艾莉西亞前輩知道小愛要來啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.97,0:05:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 想給燈里一個驚喜 就沒告訴妳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.95,0:05:03.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟艾莉西亞也是朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:10.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 妳姐姐他們呢？是一起來的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:11.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐會在天亮的時候來接我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.19,0:05:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐夫篤井因為工作關係要明天下午才來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們就能一起過除夕了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.97,0:05:23.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.94,0:05:28.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 鬢子 這個小不點女孩是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.41,0:05:31.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～ 你是氣候調節員曉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.11,0:05:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是空中郵遞員伍迪先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.61,0:05:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼妳認識我們？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼的說？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.28,0:05:39.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從燈里的郵件裡知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.22,0:05:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,郵件？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.12,0:05:41.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.39,0:05:45.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈里 曉先生很帥氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.69,0:05:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.29,0:05:48.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦？是嘛是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.56,0:05:52.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,氣候調節員為了讓AQUA的人們過得舒適
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.80,0:05:55.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而在浮島上每日奮戰著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.73,0:05:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 氣候調節員是正義的英雄哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:02.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過你在哥哥面前總是抬不起頭來吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.67,0:06:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.58,0:06:05.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為欠哥哥的錢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.28,0:06:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.44,0:06:07.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.48,0:06:08.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬢子啊…！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:12.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個可愛的孩子的說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.48,0:06:13.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡可愛了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交到個可愛的女朋友了嘛 弟弟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:18.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.49,0:06:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～ 是曉先生的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.89,0:06:22.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡可…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.43,0:06:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就找到第三個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.63,0:06:27.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小愛 找到…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了燈里郵件中出現的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.67,0:06:33.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.41,0:06:35.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.98,0:06:40.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把手伸出來好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.28,0:06:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.62,0:06:45.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.66,0:06:52.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:55.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是用新威尼斯玻璃製作的豆子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.53,0:06:56.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,豆子？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.40,0:07:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,豆子象徵著財富 據說能帶來幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.57,0:07:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在地球上的義大利
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:08.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有年末一定要吃豆子料理的習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.91,0:07:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說這個城市也繼承了那個傳統
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.14,0:07:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過玻璃做的豆子不能吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:21.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是觀光的禮物啦 很受歡迎的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.76,0:07:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要弄丟了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.42,0:07:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}別掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.83,0:07:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何？是不是有種幸福將要來臨的感覺？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當作妳跟我任性的弟弟這麼要好的謝禮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.13,0:07:36.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳就收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.33,0:07:38.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼要好啊…喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.97,0:07:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.91,0:07:43.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔…叔叔？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.54,0:07:47.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵…叔叔啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先走一步了 再會了 淑女們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.05,0:07:56.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥好像比你更帥氣…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.75,0:07:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:08:00.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 大家都到齊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩～ 晚安～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:07.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小愛 妳怎麼會在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.90,0:08:10.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想跟大家一起過除夕 就跑來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.10,0:08:14.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼遠的距離 妳可真有心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.27,0:08:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍華 這孩子是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.41,0:08:19.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳就是鬼教官晃小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.88,0:08:20.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼教官？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.01,0:08:22.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就找到第四個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 藍華！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.12,0:08:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是誤會…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:29.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈里！妳到底給小愛寫的什麼郵件啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:31.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼樣的…就是一般的郵件啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.16,0:08:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:34.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是阿魯先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.69,0:08:38.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 初次見面 我就是重力調節員阿魯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.50,0:08:40.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…重力調節員就是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在地下調節重力的工作…吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.24,0:08:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 妳說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.44,0:08:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…有一件事很難啟齒…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.48,0:08:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你對藍華到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.31,0:08:54.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了！到此為止！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.58,0:08:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 燈里 那孩子會不會太興奮了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.58,0:08:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.55,0:09:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.52,0:09:02.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 亞利亞社長 飛高高
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.66,0:09:04.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}飛啊飛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:06.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她能夠與原本只能從我的郵件中認識的人們見面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.59,0:09:06.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}飛啊飛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.79,0:09:11.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像與小說中的登場人物直接見面了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.10,0:09:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是件很讓人高興的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.43,0:09:14.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人害羞的台詞 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.40,0:09:18.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.64,0:09:21.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祖母！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.84,0:09:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您最近安好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.31,0:09:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 亞利亞社長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.58,0:09:31.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,見到你這麼有精神真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.28,0:09:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祖母
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.22,0:09:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您也來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.62,0:09:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不見了 祖母
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.36,0:09:41.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀 大家都到齊了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.29,0:09:43.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家還是像以前這麼要好 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.63,0:09:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:48.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人就是祖母嗎 好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.43,0:09:50.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是第六個人了 燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.10,0:09:54.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 是位可愛的小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.24,0:09:56.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳是燈里的朋友嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.18,0:10:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 她是從地球來的 叫小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安 祖母
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.18,0:10:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安 小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.32,0:10:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祖母 請來這邊坐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.09,0:10:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝妳 藍華
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:15.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 鬢子 那位貴婦人是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.73,0:10:20.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一位是創立了亞利亞公司的大前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.90,0:10:24.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 亞利亞社長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.04,0:10:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.97,0:10:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 鬢子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.97,0:10:27.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.67,0:10:28.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.04,0:10:30.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我馬上回來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.51,0:10:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小愛 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:37.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞利亞社長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.89,0:10:42.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小愛 不要緊吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.52,0:10:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.10,0:10:56.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起…把亞利亞社長跟丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.07,0:10:59.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題的 妳看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:02.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.22,0:11:18.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一片漆黑…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.59,0:11:21.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,足跡一直延伸到這裡面哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.97,0:12:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.41,0:12:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貓？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.82,0:12:19.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那隻貓…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:38.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.54,0:12:43.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信件真的能穿越時空 傳達心意的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.31,0:12:47.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說貓是連接過去和未來的動物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.72,0:13:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的…難道是以前的AQUA？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.89,0:13:03.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…大概是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.46,0:13:09.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不可思議…總覺得…有種熟悉的感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:15.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是…雖然是完全不瞭解的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.61,0:13:20.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說 我受到AQUA的歡迎了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 一定是這樣的 小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.25,0:13:31.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是讓人高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.53,0:13:36.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞利亞社長？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.23,0:13:41.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼東西在發光？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.47,0:13:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說…果然破了個洞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東西都掉出去了 什麼時候破的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.54,0:13:52.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:54.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是說 只要順著這些光走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能回到原來的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:14:00.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！是光的路標呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.09,0:14:03.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我們一邊撿一邊回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.06,0:14:04.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.09,0:14:11.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈里前輩她們好慢啊 不會出什麼事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.16,0:14:13.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不久就會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她們一定是到處去逛了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.27,0:14:17.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.37,0:14:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.61,0:14:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來 燈里 小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:26.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳們跑哪裡去了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.58,0:14:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.75,0:14:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AQUA
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.82,0:14:35.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳在說什麼啊？AQUA不就是這裡嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.42,0:14:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超級不知所云
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.99,0:14:43.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 小愛 妳帶了什麼可以扔的東西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.53,0:14:44.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以扔的東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.96,0:14:47.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新威尼斯除夕最盛大的活動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.87,0:14:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是在新年的凌晨零點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.50,0:14:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起用力把什麼東西扔向天空
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要是去年使用過的東西 什麼都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈里要扔什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.81,0:14:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們領航員都是扔這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.95,0:15:02.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我…扔這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.02,0:15:07.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個緞帶是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.45,0:15:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 上次來的時候繫的緞帶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為要來新威尼斯 所以就繫上它了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.36,0:15:15.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？很有紀念意義的緞帶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.57,0:15:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多要開始倒數了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.44,0:15:31.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小愛 新年的慶賀語是AUGURI BUON ANNO
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.18,0:15:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AUGURI…BUON ANNO？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.75,0:15:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 AUGURI是祝賀的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.65,0:15:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,BUON ANNO則是新年快樂的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:42.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.59,0:15:48.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年真的發生了許多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美麗的邂逅 和獨一無二的美好時光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.63,0:15:55.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的一年…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.17,0:16:05.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一想到這像寶物一樣閃閃發光的一年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.48,0:16:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就要結束了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.51,0:16:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得有點讓人感傷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.25,0:16:13.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓…讓人害羞的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:17.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是個奢侈的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.29,0:16:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.29,0:16:20.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美好的奢侈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.19,0:16:22.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}dieci(10)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.53,0:16:23.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}nove(9)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.89,0:16:24.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}otto(8)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.30,0:16:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}sette(7)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.60,0:16:27.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}sei(6)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.77,0:16:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}cinque(5)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}quattro(4)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}tre(3)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.60,0:16:32.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}due(2)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.77,0:16:34.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}uno(1)！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.76,0:16:26.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.73,0:16:27.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.67,0:16:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AUGURI BUON ANNO！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.15,0:17:56.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安 燈里 小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.89,0:17:59.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.62,0:18:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不覺就睡著了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.79,0:18:05.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是剛剛才醒的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:06.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小愛 看看後面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.67,0:18:09.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.00,0:18:11.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來接妳了 愛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.14,0:18:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小愛的姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.74,0:18:14.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 請坐在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝妳 燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.61,0:18:18.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我一坐下這孩子就會哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.58,0:18:20.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.25,0:18:24.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次見面 她的名字是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.28,0:18:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她叫做 AQUA（水星）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.15,0:18:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AQUA？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.35,0:18:29.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.12,0:18:30.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.76,0:18:32.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AQUA啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.40,0:18:42.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 AQUA真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.78,0:18:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想跟這孩子一起看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.31,0:18:55.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜歡的AQUA的新年日出
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:04.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊 AQUA 太陽要升起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.67,0:19:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是新年日出
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.03,0:19:19.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太陽的光芒讓人感覺到了溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.24,0:19:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像連內心深處也被溫暖了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.87,0:19:24.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人害羞的台詞 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:30.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望今年也是美好的一年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:32.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.18,0:19:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也這麼認為
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:35.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.75,0:19:37.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.82,0:19:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今年也會為了成為
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.93,0:19:42.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獨當一面的領航員而努力的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.19,0:19:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍華 這種話應該跟我說！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.60,0:19:45.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.24,0:19:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用全身去感受陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.87,0:19:57.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,異常耀眼而嶄新的 純白的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.94,0:20:00.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 是個嶄新的 暖洋洋的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.68,0:20:02.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,純白的一年的初始之日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.21,0:20:05.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這以後的世界將被染成什麼樣的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.15,0:20:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就看我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:08.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.62,0:20:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 愛 我們該回酒店了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.49,0:20:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳要好好地睡一覺才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.33,0:20:21.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為下午還要跟篤井姐夫會合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.07,0:20:23.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了 燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.87,0:20:25.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.37,0:20:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.81,0:20:29.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再會的說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.28,0:20:32.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:47.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小愛跟她姐姐看起來很幸福呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.86,0:20:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩跟小愛的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.29,0:20:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在她來水星做新婚旅行的時候見過的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.63,0:20:54.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.47,0:20:59.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小寶貝比照相的時候長大了許多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.80,0:21:02.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.57,0:21:06.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她能帶著孩子一起來 真是令人高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.21,0:21:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 沒想到再次相會時彼此的家人都增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.82,0:21:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.02,0:21:14.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊…
